-- Example of the area of the circle

say The area of a circle is πr².
say Which means the value of pi times (the radius of the circle squared).

wait 2


say  
say I have a circle,
say its radius is 9.
say  

wait 1

say Its area is π × 9²,
var Area_Of_The_Circle = 3.14159265358979 * 9 ** 2
say Which is ~Area_Of_The_Circle~.
